claim.claim-text:
A straddle type vehicle brake system comprising:
a front brake (31);
a rear brake (41);
a front brake operating device (50) configured to operate the front brake (31);
a rear brake operating device (60, 102) configured to operate the rear brake (41); and
an interlocking brake operating device (70, 101) configured to operate the front and rear brakes (31, 41) such that the front and rear brakes (31, 41) work in an interlocked manner.

A straddle type vehicle comprising:
a chassis (11);
a front wheel (3);
a handlebar (12) configured to control a direction of the front wheel (3); and
the straddle type vehicle brake system according to any one of claims 1 to 5,
wherein the straddle type vehicle brake system includes left and right brake levers provided on the handlebar (12) and a brake pedal as the front brake operating device (50), the rear brake operating device (60, 102) and the interlocking brake operating device (70, 101).
